text: Just South of the US/Canadian Border is located an Individually owned 44 Foot Dock / Slip with Condominium Ownership within the Semiahmoo Marina. Well Situated location close to the main gangway on the D Dock - (D6). Water and Power hookups available. Fantastic Marina with Full Laundry Facilities, Restrooms and Dockside Market/Deli. The Marina is adjacent to the popular Semiahmoo Resort, the gated Semiahmoo Neighborhood as well as the Semiahmoo Golf Course. Truly one of the finest neighborhoods in Washington State. Excellent home port for exploring the San Juan Islands, Gulf Islands and Pacific Northwest. Additionally - the boat featured in the photos can be purchased separately.

Discover this hard-to-find 3 bed/2.5 bath multi-level home in the highly desirable Edgemoor neighborhood. This quality cul de sac location is only blocks from Fairhaven Park & the Bayside Swimming Club. Enjoy the warmth of 2 free-standing gas fireplaces, great natural light, bamboo floors, & Corian countertops. Addt'l features incld attached 2-car garage w/space for workbench, sliding glass door that opens to private patio area perfect for BBQing or relaxing, & a lot that is a gardener's canvas. If that's not enough, go enjoy the views from your spacious perched deck at the rear of the property.Located near schools, parks, Fairhaven, & Chuckanut Dr, this outstanding home offers convenience & beauty of this iconic neighborhood.

Live near Lake Samish in this beautifully updated home in popular Calmor Cove. Part manufactured home, part stick-built, this home features a large, modern kitchen with plenty of counterspace, new cabinets and stainless steel appliances, and a garden window. A versatile floor plan offers plenty of living space indoors. The abundant outdoor living spaces offer private and peaceful views to enjoy nature, complementing the active lakeside lifestyle. Live where there is easy access to Lake Samish with a dock to moor your boat or lake frontage to drop in your kayak, and in a community that enjoys resort style activities all summer! Close to I-5. Potential for Seller financing!

Tucked away in a quiet cul-de-sac in Glacier Springs, this like-new chalet style home built in 2021 is surrounded by the beauty of the Mt. Baker wilderness. A thoughtful open floor plan with 2 bedrooms, laundry room, 3/4 bath on main floor & a large loft/primary room with en-suite & secret bonus loft. Enjoy high speed fiber internet, radiant heated concrete and tile floors, a/c, high-end kitchen finishes, & solid fir doors/trim. Take in the picturesque views of Slide Mountain from the expansive great room & hear the nearby creek as you relax on the tigerwood deck or in the hot tub. Situated on a spacious 1/4 acre with a direct private trail to Canyon Creek, the property backs up to many acres of protected land. A truly unique home!

Sweat equity opportunity in this spacious, well-built home ready for your updates! With 4 bedrooms and 2.5 baths on the main level, a light-filled living room with a gas fireplace, a large dining area, and a bonus room in the basement with a half bath already plumbed for a shower, this home has more to offer than meets the eye. The large lot features a fully fenced and private backyard with a covered deck, patio, garden boxes, fruit trees, and a garden shed. Ample parking is available in the front, and the nicely landscaped and split rail fenced front yard adds to the appeal of the property. A little updating will go a long way in this home. The home is priced with needed updates in mind and in as-is condition.

8.5 acres+/- of beautiful wooded land, perfect for a weekend away! Just a short drive from Everson, creating easy access to local amenities while still savoring the peace and quiet of the foothills. Don't miss this rare opportunity to own a piece of paradise in the heart of nature. Schedule a visit today!

Welcome to this charming craftsman home in the heart of Blaine! This 3 bed, 2 bath gem offers 1, 545 sq ft of well-designed living space, all on one level. Enjoy year-round comfort with mini splits (A/C) + 2 car garage. Dont miss the opportunity to make this adorable craftsman home yours its the perfect blend of style, comfort, and convenience!
Great little cozy home, large lot, detached garage and storage shed. Room for everyone. Home is sold As Is.

Investor alert! Discover the potential at 3519 Northwest Ave! Bring your toolbelt and some imagination to this restoration opportunity. Comes with possibly operational solar panels. Bus stop is directly in front of property. Close to stores, parks, and many other amenities. Home is in fixer condition and is priced to move quick!

Enjoy the Comfort and Convenience of Southside Living in this Private Ground-floor Condo nestled among a Serene Forest backdrop. This Inviting Home features 2 Spacious Bedrooms, 2 Baths and an Office/Den space. The Primary Bedroom features a spacious Ensuite and double closets. The Living Area features a Cozy Fireplace and opens to a Partially Enclosed Kitchen, Ideal for Entertaining. Step outside onto the Patio, Perfect for Relaxing and watching the wildlife. Dont miss out on this low maintenance living in the ideal setting.....Welcome Home!

A lovely Silver Beach single level home with 3 bedrooms, 1.75 bathrooms and set on a mature, fully fenced .220 acre corner lot... a haven for wildlife and plants. This home has a large living room, dining area and den with birch wood floors, and partial views of Lake Whatcom and the surrounding foothills, and a large covered porch where you can sit and enjoy the evening sun. This sought after location is a delightfully peaceful neighborhood, so bring your remodel designs and make this your place to call home.

Let the sun shine In! Beautifully renovated single story home just off the 13th fairway in the heart of Semiahmoo. Better than building from the ground up, the updates are stunning - all new LVP flooring, lighting, exterior siding, paint, windows, bathrooms and more! Floor plan is open & spacious with no wasted space. Impressive great room with vaulted ceilings is open to the kitchen and patio - great for entertaining or enjoying your own space. Brand new on-trend kitchen features new appliances, quartz counters and double island. Primary suite located on the view side with patio access and the most beautiful en-suite bathroom. 2 guest bedrooms, family room, walk-in pantry and 3 car garage complete this move-in ready house. A must see!

Come home to Salish Breeze and enjoy a peaceful & serene neighborhood. This pristine home is impressive with meticulous attention to every detail. Soaring living room ceilings, kitchen designed for a chef, and endless entertaining, at the end-of-day retreat to your enormous primary suite on main floor, laundry room is a gem. Two beds up, plus a bonus room that boasts a peak of the bay. New high end carpeting throughout. Soak in your hot tub in private backyard with play set, fruit trees and a spotless workshop w/electricity. Unparalleled condition, walking distance to beautiful Birch Bay State Park in a welcoming neighborhood. Detailed list of updates and extras available from your agent. Don't miss this cream puff.

Welcome to the finest condo living in the heart of Cordata! This exceptional 55+ ground-level home in the gated El Dorado community lives like a house without the hassle of exterior maintenance. Offering 3 spacious bedrooms &2.5 baths across 2, 133 sq. ft., you'll revel in luxurious features including radiant floor heating, a spacious kitchen with granite countertops, built in desk and a primary suite with double doors, and fireplace. Enjoy the convenience of 2 single-car garages, two patios, a formal dining room, and amenities like a clubhouse, greenhouse, dog run, and two furnished rentable condos for visitors. Secure, pet-friendly, and close to shopping, trails, and parksthis is the lifestyle you deserve.

Enjoy a luxurious life in this beautiful New Custom Built Home. From soaring high ceilings to custom built shelves in all 3 walk in closet bedrooms, it has it all! Benefit working from home with a main floor office/den room and extra large rec room downstairs w/ a wet bar.

Fantastic single-level rambler centrally located in Bellingham on a double lot. This 3 bed 1 bath home is the perfect starter or investment property. Tons of space to garden, play and more. Walking distance to Whole Foods, Fred Meyer, bus line & downtown. Newer roof, water heater and paint. Home has been well-kept and is ready for new owners!

Brand New high quality 3 bedroom 2.5 bath 4-plex in upscale multi-family neighborhood. All units have attached garages, Quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, self closing cupboards and draws in both kitchen and bathrooms, mini split heat for both heat and air conditioning, quality vinyl plank flooring throughout, 65 gallon remote controlled water heaters.

This is IT! Beautifully built lakeside New Construction rambler with luxurious finishes on a double lot (estimated $40K+ value). This gorgeous home has it all, including 2 bdrms plus spacious bonus room that lives like 3rd bdrm or the perfect office/den. Relax in the tiled shower in your primary bathroom or enjoy entertaining from your open concept living/kitchen space, complete with stainless steel appliances. W/in walking distance of Reed Lake, youll love your oversized lot, outdoor deck, and all that Glenhaven has to offer. HOA includes a club house, parks, pool, plus nearby trails. This lovely property offers the very best in Northwest lakeside living! Up to $5, 000 Buyer Credit with The Pysden Team at CrossCoutry Mortgage available.

Incredible views from Lummi Island and Bellingham Bay to Galbraith Mountain from this beautiful, well designed sun filled home. Downstairs you will find 2 bedrooms, a full bath with double vanity, a third large finished room and family room with access to the second porch and fully fenced backyard with a raised garden bed. Stay comfortable year round with one year old AC unit!

Point Roberts cozy get away cottage. Walk to everything!! Perfect location for access to Point Roberts amenities. See it today!

Your beautifully remodeled with FRESH exterior paint, single-level craftsman home featuring top-notch kitchen solid wood cabinets, elegant decorative custom concrete countertops, and a bright, open-concept living/dining/kitchen area perfect for hosting. Step into comfort with this exceptional 4 bed, 2.25 bath home featuring an open floor plan and countless upgrades. Enjoy the serenity & beauty of a territorial view overlooking Fishtrap Creek, from your private balcony. This open concept, 2 bed, 2 bath, upper level unit is a gem. NW Contemporary Craftsman with wood & stone accents, situated in extraordinary cul-de-sac in the heart of Lynden. Exceptional location! Luxurious granite counters/island in well-designed kitchen. Stunning, built for builder home on over a 1/4 acre in east Lynden! Close to town and all the amenities- but far enough to still have that peaceful, quiet town feel. No HOA! Wired and ready for hot tub and pool. On demand tankless hot water heater and A/C for comfort. This beautiful home has custom touches everywhere you look. Gorgeous sunrises and sunsets highlight Mt. Baker in the distance.
